<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ابْن مُحَمَّد الطوسي ثَنَا أَبُو حَفْص حَرْمَلَة بن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يحيى.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن كنيته أَبُو الْحسن)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٨٢٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> عَليّ بن أبي طَالب بن<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عبد الْمطلب الْهَاشِمِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>شهد بَدْرًا مَعَ رَسُول الله صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>أَخُوهُ , وَابْن عَمه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>كناه عمر بن الْخطاب رَضِي الله عَنهُ ,<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَوْلَا أَبُو الْحسن لهلك عمر.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>واستشاره فِي مَال أَتَاهُ ,<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> مَا تَقول يَا أَبَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>حسن؟ .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>١٨٢١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> رَافع بن أبي رَافع<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>الطَّائِي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>شهد غَزْوَة ذَات السلَاسِل مَعَ أبي بكر رَضِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>الله عَنهُ فِي حَيَاة النَّبِي صلى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> طَارق بن شهَاب , وَعبد الْملك بن<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>عُمَيْر وَجَمَاعَة.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>كناه البُخَارِيّ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن التَّابِعين: من كنيته أَبُو الْحسن)</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>١٨٢٢ - <span class="c2">(ق ٧٧ / أ)</span> أَبُو الْحسن: عَليّ بن<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>الْحُسَيْن بن عَليّ بن أبي طَالب.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>عَن أَبِيه , كناه مُحَمَّد بن عمر الْوَاقِدِيّ.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>١٨٢٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> مهَاجر التَّيْمِيّ.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>سَأَلَ عبد الله بن عَبَّاس.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مسعر , وكناه.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> سُفْيَان الثَّوْريّ , وَأبي الْأَحْوَص.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span>١٨٢٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> عبيد بن الْحسن ,<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span>الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبد الله بن أبي أوفى.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>كناه الْأَعْمَش.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مسعر بن كدام , وَشعْبَة بن<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>الْحجَّاج.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>١٨٢٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> هِلَال بن يسَاف.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبد الله بن عَبَّاس , وَأبي مَسْعُود<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>الْأنْصَارِيّ.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مَنْصُور بن الْمُعْتَمِر , وَعَمْرو بن مرّة<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>وكناه.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>١٨٢٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحسن:</span> عَطِيَّة بن سعد الْعَوْفِيّ ,<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>كُوفِي.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبد الله بن عَبَّاس , وَابْن عمر ,<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>وَأبي سعيد الْخُدْرِيّ.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> إِسْمَاعِيل بن أبي خَالِد , وَسليمَان<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span>الْأَعْمَش , وفراس بن يحيى.<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>